title: AN Jeunesse Évolution
text: Association Nouvelle Jeunesse Évolution, commonly known as AN Jeunesse Évolution, or simply as Jeunesse Évolution, is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> <a href="football%20team">club</a> based in <a href="Les%20Abymes">Les Abymes</a>, <a href="Guadeloupe">Guadeloupe</a>, playing in the <a href="Guadeloupe%20Division%20of%20Honor">Guadeloupe Division of Honor</a>.
